org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT m.project_id FROM members AS m INNER JOIN member_roles AS mr ON mr.member_id = m.id INNER JOIN custom_fields_roles AS cfr ON cfr.role_id = mr.role_id WHERE m.user_id = 2 AND cfr.custom_field_id = 30)
